{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775870565528,"sessionID":"ses_285e13ecaffeMp9o3UxFFIXU67","part":{"id":"prt_d7a1ecb1d001Go3yh0zrq1QBRe","messageID":"msg_d7a1ec22d001j2X4jJvym6xPnP","sessionID":"ses_285e13ecaffeMp9o3UxFFIXU67","type":"tool","tool":"task","callID":"call_0332dfc5b3e643288a6b499b","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"description":"Explore agentcube project structure","prompt":"Explore the agentcube project thoroughly. I need to understand:\n\n1. The overall project structure - what directories exist at the top level and key subdirectories\n2. Look for any existing `manifests/` directory or Helm-related files (*.yaml, Chart.yaml, values.yaml, templates/)\n3. Look for any existing design.md files or AR-XXX files to understand the format/conventions used\n4. Look for any \"AR-030\" or \"ST-1\" references in the codebase\n5. Check for any existing Helm charts, Kubernetes manifests, or deployment configurations\n6. Look at the project's README or documentation for architecture overview\n7. Check for any existing patterns in how modules are structured\n\nSearch broadly - check directories like `manifests/`, `deploy/`, `helm/`, `charts/`, `k8s/`, `infrastructure/`, etc.\n\nAlso look for any `AR-*` or `ST-*` numbered references, and any existing `design.md` files to understand the expected format.\n\nReturn a comprehensive summary of:\n- Project structure overview\n- Any existing Helm/K8s related files and their locations\n- Format conventions for design docs and AR/ST references\n- Any relevant configuration patterns already in use","subagent_type":"explore"},"output":"task_id: ses_285e110a7ffeOHSEOdpEeggQyT (for resuming to continue this task if needed)\n\n<task_result>\nI now have a comprehensive understanding of the project. Here is the full summary:\n\n---\n\n## Comprehensive Project Summary: AgentCube\n\n### 1. Project Structure Overview\n\nThe project root is at `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z` and contains:\n\n```\nagentcube/\n├── .sdd_prompt.md              # SDD prompt for design generation\n├── delta-spec.md               # Delta spec for AR-029 (SDK HTTP clients)\n├── design.md                   # Root design doc (AR-029: SDK HTTP底层客户端)\n├── go.mod / go.sum             # Go module: github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube (Go 1.25.0)\n├── project.md                  # Project context & architecture overview\n├── proposal.md                 # AR-028 proposal (SDK AgentRuntimeClient)\n├── tasks.md                    # AR-023 tasks (CLI invoke/status commands)\n├── test_spec.md                # Test specifications\n├── agentd                      # Compiled binary\n├── coverage.out                # Test coverage output\n│\n├── changes/                    # AR (Architecture Request) change directories\n│   ├── AR-001/ through AR-030/  # 30 ARs, each containing design.md, tasks.md, and optionally proposal.md, delta-spec.md\n│\n├── cmd/                        # Go binaries\n│   ├── workloadmanager/main.go\n│   ├── agentd/main.go\n│   └── picod/main.go\n│\n├── pkg/                        # Go packages\n│   ├── apis/\n│   │   ├── agents/v1alpha1/     # Sandbox types\n│   │   └── runtime/v1alpha1/    # CRD types (AgentRuntime, CodeInterpreter)\n│   ├── agentd/                  # Agentd reconciler\n│   ├── common/types/            # Shared types (SandboxInfo, etc.)\n│   ├── picod/                   # PicoD daemon\n│   └── workloadmanager/         # Workload Manager (server, handlers, reconciler)\n│\n├── client-go/                   # Generated Kubernetes client code\n│   ├── clientset/\n│   ├── informers/\n│   └── listers/\n│\n├── python-sdk/                  # Python SDK (agentcube-sdk)\n│   ├── agentcube/               # SDK package\n│   └── tests/\n│\n├── deployment/                  # Deployment module docs\n│   ├── design.md               # Detailed Helm chart design\n│   ├── spec.md\n│   └── client-go.md\n│\n├── sandbox-orchestration/       # Sandbox orchestration module docs\n│   ├── design.md               # CRD types, Go package structure, reconciler details\n│   └── spec.md\n│\n├── session-routing/             # Router/session routing module docs\n│   ├── design.md\n│   └── spec.md\n│\n├── session-store/               # Session store module docs\n│   ├── design.md\n│   └── spec.md\n│\n├── code-execution/              # Code execution module docs\n│   ├── design.md\n│   └── spec.md\n│\n├── cli-toolkit/                 # CLI toolkit module docs\n│   ├── design.md\n│   └── spec.md\n│\n├── ci-cd/                       # CI/CD module docs\n│   ├── design.md\n│   └── spec.md\n│\n├── idle-cleanup/                # Idle cleanup module docs\n│   ├── design.md\n│   └── spec.md\n│\n├── integrations/                # Integrations module docs\n│   ├── design.md\n│   └── spec.md\n│\n├── testing/                     # Testing artifacts\n│   └── agentcube_tdd_manifest.md\n│\n└── cmd/cli/examples/            # CLI agent examples (YAML metadata)\n    ├── hello-agent/agent_metadata.yaml\n    ├── math-agent/agent_metadata.yaml\n    └── java-agent/agent_metadata.yaml\n```\n\n### 2. Existing Helm/K8s Related Files\n\n**No actual Helm chart files exist in the repository yet.** There are:\n- No `manifests/` directory\n- No `Chart.yaml` files\n- No `values.yaml` files\n- No `templates/` directories\n- No `*.yaml` Kubernetes manifest files (only `agent_metadata.yaml` examples for CLI agents)\n\nHowever, **extensive documentation exists** describing the intended Helm chart:\n\n| File | Description |\n|------|-------------|\n| `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/deployment/design.md` | Complete Helm chart design: Chart.yaml fields, values.yaml key tree (271 lines), all template specs, RBAC rules, CRD definitions, Dockerfiles, Makefile targets |\n| `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/deployment/spec.md` | Deployment specification |\n| `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-030/design.md` | AR-030 design for Helm Chart (41 lines, mostly TODO placeholders) |\n| `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-030/proposal.md` | AR-030 proposal (117 lines) -- detailed scope, architecture, alternatives |\n| `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-030/delta-spec.md` | AR-030 delta spec (402 lines) -- exhaustive Gherkin-style requirements for every template |\n| `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-030/tasks.md` | AR-030 tasks (39 lines, mostly TODO placeholders) |\n\nThe intended chart structure (from AR-030 proposal):\n```\nmanifests/charts/base/\n├── Chart.yaml\n├── values.yaml\n├── crds/\n│   ├── runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh_agentruntimes.yaml\n│   └── runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh_codeinterpreters.yaml\n└── templates/\n    ├── workloadmanager.yaml\n    ├── agentcube-router.yaml\n    ├── rbac/workloadmanager.yaml\n    ├── rbac-router.yaml\n    └── volcano-agent-scheduler-development.yaml\n```\n\n### 3. Format Conventions for Design Docs and AR/ST References\n\n#### AR (Architecture Request) Directory Structure\nEach AR lives under `changes/AR-NNN/` and typically contains:\n- `design.md` -- Technical design with architecture, data structures, API contracts, error handling, testing strategy\n- `tasks.md` -- Task breakdown with T-NNN numbered items, checkboxes, verification criteria, dependency graphs\n- `proposal.md` -- (Optional) Purpose, scope, impact analysis, alternatives considered, acceptance criteria\n- `delta-spec.md` -- (Optional) Gherkin-style requirement/spec scenarios for incremental changes\n\n#### Design Document Format (from AR-001 as the exemplar)\n```markdown\n# AR-NNN: Title -- Design/设计说明\n\n## 1. 架构 (Architecture)\n### 1.1 定位 (Purpose/Positioning)\n### 1.2 包结构 (Package Structure)\n### 1.3 依赖关系 (Dependencies)\n### 1.4 代码生成工具链 (Code Generation Toolchain)\n\n## 2. 数据结构 (Data Structures)\n### 2.x Type definitions with Go code blocks\n### 2.x Data structure relationship diagrams (ASCII trees)\n\n## 3. API 契约 (API Contracts)\n### 3.x GVK/GVR tables\n### 3.x REST endpoints\n### 3.x Example YAML\n### 3.x Generated interfaces\n\n## 4. 错误处理 (Error Handling)\n### 4.x Validation errors, application errors, defaults, concurrency\n\n## 5. 测试策略 (Testing Strategy)\n### 5.x Unit test code examples\n### 5.x Test file layout\n### 5.x Test commands\n### 5.x TDD cross-reference table\n\n## 6. 实现步骤 (Implementation Steps)\n### 6.x File creation order\n### 6.x Verification checklist\n\n## 7. 后续变更 (Follow-up Changes)\n```\n\n#### Module-Level Design Format (non-AR)\nModules like `deployment/`, `sandbox-orchestration/`, `session-routing/` use a simpler format:\n```markdown\n# Module Name -- Design\n\n## Module / Package sections\n## Code structures (Go types, configs, routes)\n## Tables for flags, env vars, endpoints\n```\n\n#### ST (Stage) References\n- **ST-1** = Proposal stage\n- Found references:\n  - `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/.sdd_prompt.md` line 463: `[Stage ST-1 completed]`\n  - `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-003/tasks.md` line 3: `> **Stage**: ST-1 (Proposal)`\n  - `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/testing/agentcube_tdd_manifest.md` line 23: `**Test-ST-1**`\n  - `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/test_spec.md` line 16: `TestCase-ST-001`\n\n#### Tasks Format\n```markdown\n# AR-NNN Title — Tasks\n\n> **Stage**: ST-N (Stage Name)\n> **Module**: module_name\n> **Language**: Go/Python/YAML\n> **Size**: S/M/L\n\n## T-NNN: Task Title\n- [ ] T-NNN.NN Verification step\n**Verification**: command to verify\n\n## Dependency Graph (ASCII)\n## Parallelizable Groups (table)\n## Acceptance Criteria (table)\n```\n\n### 4. AR-030 and ST-1 References\n\n**AR-030** is the Helm Chart AR:\n- Title: \"Helm Chart 模板与 Values\"\n- Module: `manifests`\n- Language: YAML\n- Size: L\n- Status: Design doc has TODO placeholders; tasks.md has TODO placeholders; proposal.md and delta-spec.md are fully written\n- The delta-spec.md is extremely detailed with 402 lines of Gherkin-style requirements\n\n**ST-1** is the \"Proposal\" stage, referenced in:\n- AR-003 tasks.md header\n- `.sdd_prompt.md` completion marker\n- Test specifications\n\n### 5. Existing Configuration Patterns\n\n#### Go Module\n- Module: `github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube`\n- Go version: 1.25.0\n- Key dependencies: Gin, go-redis/v9, valkey-go, k8s.io/api v0.34.1, controller-runtime v0.22.2, golang-jwt/v5\n\n#### Kubernetes API Group\n- Group: `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh`\n- Version: `v1alpha1`\n- CRDs: `AgentRuntime`, `CodeInterpreter`\n- External: `agents.x-k8s.io/v1alpha1` (Sandbox), `extensions.agents.x-k8s.io/v1alpha1` (SandboxClaim, etc.)\n\n#### Code Generation\n- `controller-gen` v0.17.2 for DeepCopy + CRD YAML\n- `k8s.io/code-generator` v0.34.1 for client-go\n- Entry: `make gen-all` -> `generate` + `gen-client`\n\n#### Makefile Key Targets\n- `gen-crd` -> outputs to `manifests/charts/base/crds/`\n- `build`, `build-router`, `build-agentd`, `build-all`\n- `docker-build`, `docker-build-router`, `docker-build-picod`\n- `e2e` -> runs `test/e2e/run_e2e.sh`\n- Image registry: `ghcr.io/volcano-sh`\n\n#### Helm Install Pattern (from E2E script)\n```bash\nhelm upgrade --install agentcube manifests/charts/base \\\n  --namespace \"${AGENTCUBE_NAMESPACE}\" --create-namespace \\\n  --set redis.addr=\"redis.${AGENTCUBE_NAMESPACE}.svc.cluster.local:6379\" \\\n  --set redis.password=\"\" \\\n  --set workloadmanager.image.repository=\"workloadmanager\" \\\n  --set workloadmanager.image.tag=\"latest\" \\\n  --set-json 'workloadmanager.extraEnv=[...]' \\\n  --set router.image.repository=\"agentcube-router\" \\\n  --set router.image.tag=\"latest\" \\\n  --set router.rbac.create=true \\\n  --set router.serviceAccountName=\"agentcube-router\" \\\n  --wait\n```\n\n#### Values Defaults (from deployment/design.md)\n| Component | Key Defaults |\n|-----------|-------------|\n| Router | `replicas: 1`, image `ghcr.io/volcano-sh/agentcube-router:latest`, service `ClusterIP:8080`, resources `100m-500m CPU, 128Mi-512Mi mem` |\n| WorkloadManager | `replicas: 1`, image `ghcr.io/volcano-sh/workloadmanager:latest`, service `ClusterIP:8080`, same resource defaults |\n| Volcano | `enabled: false`, image `ghcr.io/volcano-sh/vc-agent-scheduler:latest` |\n| Redis | `addr: \"\"`, `password: \"\"` (must be provided at install) |\n\n### 6. Key Architectural Components\n\n```\nClient / SDK / CLI\n  -> Router (Deployment :8080)\n     <-> Redis/Valkey (session store)\n     -> WorkloadManager (Service :8080)\n        <-> Redis/Valkey\n        -> K8s API: CRDs, Sandbox, Pod, Secret, TokenReview\n  Sandbox Pods (with optional PicoD daemon)\n  Agentd (idle cleanup controller)\n  Optional: Volcano vc-agent-scheduler\n```\n\n### 7. Summary of What Exists vs. What Needs to Be Created\n\n| Artifact | Status |\n|----------|--------|\n| `manifests/charts/base/Chart.yaml` | **Does NOT exist** -- fully specified in delta-spec.md |\n| `manifests/charts/base/values.yaml` | **Does NOT exist** -- fully specified in deployment/design.md |\n| `manifests/charts/base/templates/workloadmanager.yaml` | **Does NOT exist** -- fully specified in delta-spec.md |\n| `manifests/charts/base/templates/agentcube-router.yaml` | **Does NOT exist** -- fully specified in delta-spec.md |\n| `manifests/charts/base/templates/rbac/workloadmanager.yaml` | **Does NOT exist** -- RBAC rules fully documented |\n| `manifests/charts/base/templates/rbac-router.yaml` | **Does NOT exist** -- fully specified in delta-spec.md |\n| `manifests/charts/base/templates/volcano-agent-scheduler-development.yaml` | **Does NOT exist** -- fully specified in delta-spec.md |\n| `manifests/charts/base/crds/*.yaml` | **Do NOT exist** -- CRD schemas fully documented in deployment/design.md |\n| AR-030 design.md | **Exists** but contains TODO placeholders |\n| AR-030 tasks.md | **Exists** but contains TODO placeholders |\n| AR-030 proposal.md | **Exists** and is complete (117 lines) |\n| AR-030 delta-spec.md | **Exists** and is complete (402 lines) |\n</task_result>","metadata":{"sessionId":"ses_285e110a7ffeOHSEOdpEeggQyT","model":{"modelID":"qwen3.6-plus","providerID":"alibaba-cn"},"truncated":false},"title":"Explore agentcube project structure","time":{"start":1775870340948,"end":1775870565523}}}}
