{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775870832537,"sessionID":"ses_285e13ecaffeMp9o3UxFFIXU67","part":{"id":"prt_d7a2375f0001UcH5Z7Cye06jiB","messageID":"msg_d7a235e00001cLpCk1gWA66RUJ","sessionID":"ses_285e13ecaffeMp9o3UxFFIXU67","type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"call_8761772f375343018f96da17","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"content":"# AR-030: Helm Chart 模板与 Values — Design/设计说明\n\n## 1. 架构 (Architecture)\n\n### 1.1 定位 (Purpose/Positioning)\n\n`manifests/charts/base` 是 AgentCube 控制面栈的 Helm Chart，提供参数化的 Kubernetes 资源模板，支持一键安装、升级和回滚。Chart 驱动 Workload Manager、Router、可选 Volcano 调度器的完整部署生命周期，通过 `values.yaml` 集中管理所有可配置参数（镜像、副本数、资源配额、Redis 连接、环境变量覆盖）。\n\nChart 是 E2E 测试、生产部署、开发者本地 Kind 集群的统一入口，消除手动编辑 YAML 的需求。\n\n### 1.2 包结构 (Package Layout)\n\n```\nmanifests/charts/base/\n├── Chart.yaml                              # Chart 元数据 (apiVersion v1, name agentcube, version 0.1.0)\n├── values.yaml                             # 默认配置值树 (Redis, Router, WorkloadManager, Volcano)\n├── crds/\n│   ├── runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh_agentruntimes.yaml    # AgentRuntime CRD (v1alpha1, Namespaced)\n│   └── runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh_codeinterpreters.yaml # CodeInterpreter CRD (v1alpha1, Namespaced)\n└── templates/\n    ├── workloadmanager.yaml                # WM Deployment + Service\n    ├── agentcube-router.yaml               # Router Deployment + Service\n    ├── rbac/\n    │   └── workloadmanager.yaml            # WM ServiceAccount + ClusterRole + ClusterRoleBinding\n    ├── rbac-router.yaml                    # 可选 Router ServiceAccount + Role + RoleBinding\n    └── volcano-agent-scheduler-development.yaml  # 可选 Volcano 调度器全套资源\n```\n\n### 1.3 依赖关系 (Dependencies)\n\n```\nHelm Chart (manifests/charts/base)\n  ├── 外部依赖\n  │   ├── Helm 3                          # Chart 打包与安装\n  │   ├── Kubernetes 1.28+                # CRD 注册、Deployment/Service/RBAC 创建\n  │   ├── Redis/Valkey (外部实例)          # 地址和密码通过 values 提供\n  │   └── agent-sandbox CRDs (外部)        # WM ClusterRole 引用 agents.x-k8s.io API group\n  │\n  ├── 构建产物依赖\n  │   ├── make gen-crd                    # 产出 manifests/charts/base/crds/*.yaml\n  │   ├── docker-build                    # workloadmanager 镜像\n  │   ├── docker-build-router             # agentcube-router 镜像\n  │   └── docker-build-picod              # picod 镜像 (sandbox 内使用)\n  │\n  ├──→ helm template                      渲染所有模板为 Kubernetes YAML\n  ├──→ helm upgrade --install             安装/升级到目标集群\n  ├──→ kubectl apply --dry-run=client     验证渲染结果有效性\n  └──→ test/e2e/run_e2e.sh               E2E 测试通过 helm install 部署\n```\n\n### 1.4 组件部署形态 (Component Deployment Shape)\n\n| 组件 | Kind | Service | Port | Health Endpoint | 条件渲染 |\n|------|------|---------|------|-----------------|----------|\n| Workload Manager | Deployment + Service | `workloadmanager` | 8080 | `GET /health` (liveness 10s, readiness 5s) | 始终渲染 |\n| Router | Deployment + Service | `agentcube-router` | 8080 | `GET /health/live` + `/health/ready` (1s initial, 2s period) | 始终渲染 |\n| Volcano Scheduler | Deployment + Service | `volcano-agent-scheduler-service` | 8080 | — | `volcano.scheduler.enabled` |\n| WM RBAC | SA + ClusterRole + ClusterRoleBinding | — | — | — | 始终渲染 |\n| Router RBAC | SA + Role + RoleBinding | — | — | — | `router.rbac.create` |\n\n### 1.5 代码生成工具链 (Code Generation Toolchain)\n\n| 工具 | 版本 | 用途 |\n|------|------|------|\n| controller-gen | v0.17.2 | 从 Go 类型 kubebuilder 标记生成 CRD YAML 到 `manifests/charts/base/crds/` |\n| Helm | 3.x | Chart 模板渲染、安装、升级、回滚 |\n\nCRD 生成入口：`make gen-crd` → `controller-gen crd paths=./pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/... output:crd:dir=manifests/charts/base/crds`。\n\n---\n\n## 2. 数据结构 (Data Structures)\n\n### 2.1 Chart.yaml 元数据\n\n| 字段 | 值 | 说明 |\n|------|-----|------|\n| `apiVersion` | `v1` | Helm 3 兼容，当前 scope 无需 v2 |\n| `name` | `agentcube` | Chart 名称 |\n| `description` | `A Helm chart for AgentCube` | 简短描述 |\n| `version` | `0.1.0` | Chart 语义化版本 |\n| `appVersion` | `1.0.0` | 应用版本 |\n\n### 2.2 values.yaml 完整键树\n\n```yaml\n# imagePullSecrets — 私有镜像仓库认证\nimagePullSecrets: []\n# nameOverride — 覆盖 chart 名称用于资源命名\nnameOverride: \"\"\n# fullnameOverride — 完全覆盖资源名称前缀\nfullnameOverride: \"\"\n\n# Redis/Valkey 连接配置\n# 注意: 以下两个值必须在安装时通过 --set 提供\nredis:\n  addr: \"\"       # Redis 地址, 例: redis.agentcube.svc.cluster.local:6379\n  password: \"\"   # Redis 密码, 可为空字符串\n\n# Router 组件配置\nrouter:\n  replicas: 1\n  image:\n    repository: ghcr.io/volcano-sh/agentcube-router\n    pullPolicy: IfNotPresent\n    tag: latest\n  service:\n    type: ClusterIP\n    port: 8080\n    targetPort: 8080\n  resources:\n    limits:\n      cpu: 500m\n      memory: 512Mi\n    requests:\n      cpu: 100m\n      memory: 128Mi\n  config: {}\n  extraEnv: []\n  serviceAccountName: \"\"\n  rbac:\n    create: false\n\n# Workload Manager 组件配置\nworkloadmanager:\n  replicas: 1\n  image:\n    repository: ghcr.io/volcano-sh/workloadmanager\n    pullPolicy: IfNotPresent\n    tag: latest\n  service:\n    type: ClusterIP\n    port: 8080\n  resources:\n    limits:\n      cpu: 500m\n      memory: 512Mi\n    requests:\n      cpu: 100m\n      memory: 128Mi\n  extraEnv: []\n\n# Volcano 调度器配置 (可选)\nvolcano:\n  scheduler:\n    enabled: false\n    replicas: 1\n    image:\n      repository: ghcr.io/volcano-sh/vc-agent-scheduler\n      pullPolicy: IfNotPresent\n      tag: latest\n```\n\n### 2.3 values.yaml 键树关系图\n\n```\nvalues.yaml\n├── imagePullSecrets: []                  # 全局: 镜像拉取密钥\n├── nameOverride: \"\"                      # 全局: 名称覆盖\n├── fullnameOverride: \"\"                  # 全局: 全名覆盖\n├── redis\n│   ├── addr: \"\"                          # 必填: Redis 地址 (安装时提供)\n│   └── password: \"\"                      # 可选: Redis 密码\n├── router\n│   ├── replicas: 1                       # 副本数\n│   ├── image\n│   │   ├── repository: ghcr.io/volcano-sh/agentcube-router\n│   │   ├── pullPolicy: IfNotPresent\n│   │   └── tag: latest\n│   ├── service\n│   │   ├── type: ClusterIP\n│   │   ├── port: 8080\n│   │   └── targetPort: 8080\n│   ├── resources\n│   │   ├── limits: {cpu: 500m, memory: 512Mi}\n│   │   └── requests: {cpu: 100m, memory: 128Mi}\n│   ├── config: {}                        # 预留配置对象\n│   ├── extraEnv: []                      # 额外环境变量\n│   ├── serviceAccountName: \"\"            # 可选 SA 名称\n│   └── rbac\n│       └── create: false                 # 是否创建 Router RBAC\n├── workloadmanager\n│   ├── replicas: 1\n│   ├── image\n│   │   ├── repository: ghcr.io/volcano-sh/workloadmanager\n│   │   ├── pullPolicy: IfNotPresent\n│   │   └── tag: latest\n│   ├── service\n│   │   ├── type: ClusterIP\n│   │   └── port: 8080\n│   ├── resources\n│   │   ├── limits: {cpu: 500m, memory: 512Mi}\n│   │   └── requests: {cpu: 100m, memory: 128Mi}\n│   └── extraEnv: []\n└── volcano\n    └── scheduler\n        ├── enabled: false                # 是否启用 Volcano 调度器\n        ├── replicas: 1\n        └── image\n            ├── repository: ghcr.io/volcano-sh/vc-agent-scheduler\n            ├── pullPolicy: IfNotPresent\n            └── tag: latest\n```\n\n### 2.4 模板变量映射 (Template Variable Mapping)\n\n#### 2.4.1 环境变量注入矩阵\n\n| 组件 | 环境变量 | 来源 | 模板表达式 |\n|------|----------|------|-----------|\n| Workload Manager | `AGENTCUBE_NAMESPACE` | Pod 元数据 | `fieldRef: metadata.namespace` |\n| Workload Manager | `REDIS_ADDR` | values | `{{ .Values.redis.addr }}` |\n| Workload Manager | `REDIS_PASSWORD` | values | `{{ .Values.redis.password }}` |\n| Workload Manager | `extraEnv[*]` | values | `{{- range .Values.workloadmanager.extraEnv }}` |\n| Router | `AGENTCUBE_NAMESPACE` | Pod 元数据 | `fieldRef: metadata.namespace` |\n| Router | `REDIS_ADDR` | values | `{{ .Values.redis.addr }}` |\n| Router | `REDIS_PASSWORD` | values | `{{ .Values.redis.password }}` |\n| Router | `WORKLOAD_MANAGER_URL` | 自动推导 | `http://workloadmanager.{{ .Release.Namespace }}.svc.cluster.local:{{ .Values.workloadmanager.service.port }}` |\n| Router | `extraEnv[*]` | values | `{{- range .Values.router.extraEnv }}` |\n| Volcano | `AGENTCUBE_NAMESPACE` | Pod 元数据 | `fieldRef: metadata.namespace` |\n\n#### 2.4.2 容器参数映射\n\n| 组件 | 参数 | 来源 | 模板表达式 |\n|------|------|------|-----------|\n| Workload Manager | `--port` | values | `--port={{ .Values.workloadmanager.service.port }}` |\n| Workload Manager | `--runtime-class-name=` | 硬编码 | `--runtime-class-name=` (空值) |\n| Router | `--port` | values | `--port={{ .Values.router.service.targetPort }}` |\n| Router | `--debug` | 硬编码 | `--debug` |\n| Volcano | `--scheduler-name=agent-scheduler` | 硬编码 | `--scheduler-name=agent-scheduler` |\n\n### 2.5 RBAC 规则定义 (RBAC Rules)\n\n#### 2.5.1 ClusterRole `workloadmanager` (始终渲染)\n\n| apiGroups | resources | verbs | 说明 |\n|-----------|-----------|-------|------|\n| `agents.x-k8s.io` | `sandboxes` | `get,list,watch,create,update,patch,delete` | agent-sandbox 沙箱管理 |\n| `extensions.agents.x-k8s.io` | `sandboxclaims` | `get,list,watch,create,update,patch,delete` | 沙箱声明 |\n| `extensions.agents.x-k8s.io` | `sandboxtemplates` | `get,list,watch,create,update,patch,delete` | 沙箱模板 |\n| `extensions.agents.x-k8s.io` | `sandboxwarmpools` | `get,list,watch,create,update,patch,delete` | 沙箱预热池 |\n| `extensions.agents.x-k8s.io` | `sandboxwarmpools/status` | `get,update,patch` | 预热池状态 |\n| `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh` | `codeinterpreters` | `get,list,watch,create,update,patch,delete` | CodeInterpreter CRD |\n| `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh` | `codeinterpreters/status` | `get,update,patch` | CodeInterpreter 状态 |\n| `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh` | `codeinterpreters/finalizers` | `update` | CodeInterpreter finalizer |\n| `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh` | `agentruntimes` | `get,list,watch` | AgentRuntime CRD (只读) |\n| `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh` | `agentruntimes/status` | `update,patch` | AgentRuntime 状态 |\n| `\"\"` | `pods` | `get,list,watch` | Pod 查询 |\n| `\"\"` | `secrets` | `get,list,watch,create,update,patch,delete` | Secret 管理 |\n| `authentication.k8s.io` | `tokenreviews` | `create` | 认证 Token 审查 |\n\n#### 2.5.2 Role `router` (条件渲染: `router.rbac.create`)\n\n| apiGroups | resources | verbs | 说明 |\n|-----------|-----------|-------|------|\n| `\"\"` | `secrets` | `get,list,watch,create,update,patch,delete` | 命名空间级 Secret 管理 |\n\n#### 2.5.3 ClusterRole `volcano-agent-scheduler` (条件渲染: `volcano.scheduler.enabled`)\n\n| apiGroups | resources | verbs |\n|-----------|-----------|-------|\n| `apiextensions.k8s.io` | `customresourcedefinitions` | `create,get,list,watch,delete` |\n| `\"\"` | `events` | `create,list,watch,update,patch` |\n| `\"\"` | `pods` | `get,list,watch,patch,delete` |\n| `\"\"` | `pods/status` | `update` |\n| `\"\"` | `pods/binding` | `create` |\n| `\"\"` | `persistentvolumeclaims` | `list,watch,update` |\n| `\"\"` | `persistentvolumes` | `list,watch,update` |\n| `\"\"` | `namespaces,services,replicationcontrollers` | `list,watch,get` |\n| `\"\"` | `resourcequotas` | `list,watch` |\n| `\"\"` | `nodes` | `get,list,watch,update,patch` |\n| `storage.k8s.io` | `storageclasses,csinodes,csidrivers,csistoragecapacities,volumeattachments` | `list,watch` |\n| `policy` | `poddisruptionbudgets` | `list,watch` |\n| `scheduling.k8s.io` | `priorityclasses` | `get,list,watch` |\n| `scheduling.incubator.k8s.io`, `scheduling.volcano.sh` | `podgroups` | `list,watch,update` |\n| `\"\"` | `configmaps` | `get,list,watch,create,delete,update` |\n| `apps` | `daemonsets,replicasets,statefulsets` | `list,watch,get` |\n| `coordination.k8s.io` | `leases` | `get,create,update,watch` |\n| `resource.k8s.io` | `resourceclaims` | `get,list,watch,create,update,patch` |\n| `resource.k8s.io` | `resourceclaims/status` | `update` |\n| `resource.k8s.io` | `deviceclasses,resourceslices` | `get,list,watch,create` |\n| `shard.volcano.sh` | `nodeshards` | `list,watch,get,update` |\n\n### 2.6 CRD 定义 (CRD Definitions)\n\n#### 2.6.1 AgentRuntime CRD\n\n| 属性 | 值 |\n|------|-----|\n| 文件名 | `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh_agentruntimes.yaml` |\n| CRD 名称 | `agentruntimes.runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh` |\n| API Group | `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh` |\n| Version | `v1alpha1` (served + storage) |\n| Scope | `Namespaced` |\n| 注解 | `controller-gen.kubebuilder.io/version: v0.17.2` |\n| PrinterColumn | `Age` (date, `.metadata.creationTimestamp`) |\n| Subresources | `status` |\n| spec.required | `maxSessionDuration`, `podTemplate`, `sessionTimeout`, `targetPort` |\n\n**关键 spec 字段：**\n\n| 字段 | 类型 | 默认值 | 说明 |\n|------|------|--------|------|\n| `maxSessionDuration` | string (duration) | `8h` | 会话最大存活时间 |\n| `sessionTimeout` | string (duration) | `15m` | 会话空闲超时 |\n| `targetPort` | array of port objects | — | 端口列表 (required: `port`, `protocol` enum HTTP/HTTPS) |\n| `podTemplate` | object (PodSpec-shaped) | — | 沙箱 Pod 模板 (必填) |\n\n#### 2.6.2 CodeInterpreter CRD\n\n| 属性 | 值 |\n|------|-----|\n| 文件名 | `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh_codeinterpreters.yaml` |\n| CRD 名称 | `codeinterpreters.runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh` |\n| API Group | `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh` |\n| Version | `v1alpha1` (served + storage) |\n| Scope | `Namespaced` |\n| 注解 | `controller-gen.kubebuilder.io/version: v0.17.2` |\n| Subresources | `status` |\n| spec.required | `template` |\n\n**关键 spec 字段：**\n\n| 字段 | 类型 | 默认值 | 说明 |\n|------|------|--------|------|\n| `authMode` | enum `picod\\|none` | `picod` | 认证模式 |\n| `maxSessionDuration` | string (duration) | `8h` | 会话最大存活时间 |\n| `sessionTimeout` | string (duration) | `15m` | 会话空闲超时 |\n| `ports` | array of TargetPort | — | 端口列表 |\n| `template` | object | — | 容器模板 (image, command, args, env, resources, runtimeClassName) |\n| `warmPoolSize` | int32 | — | 预热池大小 (可选) |\n\n### 2.7 Volcano ConfigMap 结构\n\n```yaml\napiVersion: v1\nkind: ConfigMap\nmetadata:\n  name: volcano-agent-scheduler-configmap\ndata:\n  agent-scheduler.conf: |\n    actions: \"allocate\"\n    tiers:\n      - plugins:\n          - name: predicates\n          - name: nodeorder\n```\n\n---\n\n## 3. API 契约 (API Contracts)\n\n### 3.1 Helm 安装契约\n\n#### 3.1.1 最小安装命令\n\n```bash\nhelm upgrade --install agentcube manifests/charts/base \\\n  --namespace agentcube \\\n  --create-namespace \\\n  --set redis.addr=redis.agentcube.svc.cluster.local:6379 \\\n  --set redis.password=pass \\\n  --wait\n```\n\n#### 3.1.2 E2E 测试安装命令 (Kind 集群)\n\n```bash\nhelm upgrade --install agentcube manifests/charts/base \\\n  --namespace \"${AGENTCUBE_NAMESPACE}\" \\\n  --create-namespace \\\n  --set redis.addr=\"redis.${AGENTCUBE_NAMESPACE}.svc.cluster.local:6379\" \\\n  --set redis.password=\"\" \\\n  --set workloadmanager.image.repository=\"workloadmanager\" \\\n  --set workloadmanager.image.tag=\"latest\" \\\n  --set-json 'workloadmanager.extraEnv=[{\"name\":\"REDIS_PASSWORD_REQUIRED\",\"value\":\"false\"},{\"name\":\"JWT_KEY_SECRET_NAMESPACE\",\"value\":\"agentcube\"}]' \\\n  --set router.image.repository=\"agentcube-router\" \\\n  --set router.image.tag=\"latest\" \\\n  --set router.rbac.create=true \\\n  --set router.serviceAccountName=\"agentcube-router\" \\\n  --set-json 'router.extraEnv=[{\"name\":\"REDIS_PASSWORD_REQUIRED\",\"value\":\"false\"}]' \\\n  --wait\n```\n\n#### 3.1.3 完整功能安装命令\n\n```bash\nhelm upgrade --install agentcube manifests/charts/base \\\n  --namespace production \\\n  --create-namespace \\\n  --set redis.addr=redis.production.svc.cluster.local:6379 \\\n  --set redis.password=secret123 \\\n  --set workloadmanager.replicas=3 \\\n  --set workloadmanager.image.tag=v1.1.0 \\\n  --set router.replicas=2 \\\n  --set router.rbac.create=true \\\n  --set router.serviceAccountName=agentcube-router \\\n  --set volcano.scheduler.enabled=true \\\n  --set-json 'imagePullSecrets=[{\"name\":\"ghcr-pull-secret\"}]' \\\n  --set-json 'workloadmanager.extraEnv=[{\"name\":\"LOG_LEVEL\",\"value\":\"info\"}]' \\\n  --wait\n```\n\n### 3.2 模板渲染契约\n\n#### 3.2.1 命名空间作用域\n\n所有命名空间级资源必须使用 `{{ .Release.Namespace }}` 作为 `metadata.namespace`，不得使用硬编码值：\n\n| 资源 | Namespace 来源 |\n|------|---------------|\n| Deployment/workloadmanager | `{{ .Release.Namespace }}` |\n| Service/workloadmanager | `{{ .Release.Namespace }}` |\n| ServiceAccount/workloadmanager | `{{ .Release.Namespace }}` |\n| Deployment/agentcube-router | `{{ .Release.Namespace }}` |\n| Service/agentcube-router | `{{ .Release.Namespace }}` |\n| ConfigMap/volcano-agent-scheduler-configmap | `{{ .Release.Namespace }}` |\n| Service/volcano-agent-scheduler-service | `{{ .Release.Namespace }}` |\n| Deployment/volcano-agent-scheduler | `{{ .Release.Namespace }}` |\n\nClusterRole 和 ClusterRoleBinding 为集群级资源，无 namespace 字段。\n\n#### 3.2.2 资源选择器契约\n\n| Deployment | Service Selector |\n|------------|-----------------|\n| `workloadmanager` | `app: workloadmanager` |\n| `agentcube-router` | `app: agentcube-router` |\n| `volcano-agent-scheduler` | `app: volcano-agent-scheduler` |\n\n#### 3.2.3 容器端口命名\n\n| 组件 | 端口名 | 端口值 |\n|------|--------|--------|\n| Workload Manager | `http` | `{{ .Values.workloadmanager.service.port }}` |\n| Router | — | `{{ .Values.router.service.targetPort }}` |\n| Volcano | — | `8080` |\n\n### 3.3 条件渲染契约\n\n| 模板 | 条件 | 渲染产物 |\n|------|------|----------|\n| `rbac-router.yaml` | `{{- if .Values.router.rbac.create }}` | ServiceAccount + Role + RoleBinding |\n| `volcano-agent-scheduler-development.yaml` | `{{- if .Values.volcano.scheduler.enabled }}` | ServiceAccount + ConfigMap + ClusterRole + ClusterRoleBinding + Service + Deployment |\n\n#### 3.3.1 Router RBAC 名称解析\n\n当 `router.rbac.create` 为 true 时，所有 RBAC 资源名称为：\n```\n{{ .Values.router.serviceAccountName | default \"agentcube-router\" }}\n```\n\n#### 3.3.2 Router serviceAccountName 条件注入\n\nRouter Deployment 的 `serviceAccountName` 仅在值非空时设置：\n```yaml\n{{- if .Values.router.serviceAccountName }}\nserviceAccountName: {{ .Values.router.serviceAccountName }}\n{{- end }}\n```\n\n### 3.4 nameOverride / fullnameOverride 契约\n\nChart 支持标准 Helm 命名覆盖模式：\n\n| 值 | 行为 |\n|----|------|\n| 默认 (空) | 资源使用组件固定名称 (`workloadmanager`, `agentcube-router`) |\n| `fullnameOverride` 非空 | 适用资源使用 `fullnameOverride` 作为名称前缀 |\n| `nameOverride` 非空 | 适用资源使用 `nameOverride` 作为名称覆盖 |\n\n命名辅助函数 (推荐定义在 `_helpers.tpl` 中):\n```\n{{- define \"agentcube.fullname\" -}}\n{{- if .Values.fullnameOverride }}\n{{- .Values.fullnameOverride | trunc 63 | trimSuffix \"-\" }}\n{{- else }}\n{{- $name := default .Chart.Name .Values.nameOverride }}\n{{- printf \"%s-%s\" .Release.Name $name | trunc 63 | trimSuffix \"-\" }}\n{{- end }}\n{{- end }}\n```\n\n### 3.5 imagePullSecrets 契约\n\n当 `imagePullSecrets` 非空时，所有 Deployment 的 `spec.template.spec.imagePullSecrets` 应注入：\n```yaml\n{{- with .Values.imagePullSecrets }}\nimagePullSecrets:\n  {{- toYaml . | nindent 2 }}\n{{- end }}\n```\n\n---\n\n## 4. 错误处理 (Error Handling)\n\n### 4.1 模板渲染错误\n\n| 场景 | 表现 | 处理方式 |\n|------|------|----------|\n| values.yaml 语法错误 | `helm template` 报错 YAML parse error | 安装前通过 `helm lint` 捕获 |\n| 模板语法错误 | `helm template` 报错 template rendering failed | 开发阶段通过 `helm template` dry-run 发现 |\n| 缺少必需 values | 渲染出空字符串 (如 `REDIS_ADDR=`) | values.yaml 注释标明必填；安装命令文档明确 `--set redis.addr=...` |\n| 类型不匹配 | Helm 类型转换失败 (如 string 用于 int 字段) | values.yaml 使用正确类型；`helm lint` 可检测部分问题 |\n\n### 4.2 安装时验证错误\n\n| 场景 | Helm 行为 | 预期错误信息 |\n|------|----------|-------------|\n| CRD 已存在且 schema 不兼容 | `helm install` 失败 | `existing resource conflicts with existing CRD` |\n| RBAC 资源权限不足 | `helm install` 失败 | `clusterroles.rbac.authorization.k8s.io is forbidden` |\n| 命名空间不存在 (无 --create-namespace) | `helm install` 失败 | `namespaces \"xxx\" not found` |\n| 镜像拉取失败 | Pod 进入 `ImagePullBackOff` | 事件日志: `Failed to pull image` |\n\n### 4.3 运行时错误处理\n\n#### 4.3.1 健康探针失败\n\n| 组件 | 探针 | 失败行为 |\n|------|------|----------|\n| Workload Manager | liveness `/health` (10s initial, 10s period) | 容器重启 |\n| Workload Manager | readiness `/health` (5s initial, 5s period) | 从 Service endpoints 移除 |\n| Router | liveness `/health/live` (1s initial, 2s period) | 容器重启 |\n| Router | readiness `/health/ready` (1s initial, 2s period) | 从 Service endpoints 移除 |\n\n#### 4.3.2 Redis 连接失败\n\n| 场景 | 影响 | 表现 |\n|------|------|------|\n| `redis.addr` 为空 | WM/Router 启动时无法连接 Redis | 健康探针失败 → 容器重启循环 |\n| `redis.password` 错误 | Redis 认证失败 | 日志显示 auth error；健康探针失败 |\n| Redis 服务不可达 | 会话存储不可用 | Router 无法路由会话；WM 无法管理沙箱状态 |\n\n#### 4.3.3 WORKLOAD_MANAGER_URL 解析失败\n\n| 场景 | 影响 |\n|------|------|\n| Workload Manager Service 未就绪 | Router 无法转发请求 → 502/503 |\n| 命名空间不匹配 (多集群场景) | DNS 解析失败 → Router 启动异常 |\n\n### 4.4 升级错误处理\n\n| 场景 | Helm 行为 | 恢复策略 |\n|------|----------|----------|\n| 新 values 导致模板渲染失败 | `helm upgrade` 回滚到上一版本 | 检查 `helm history`，修复 values 后重试 |\n| CRD schema 变更不兼容 | CRD 更新失败，其余资源可能已更新 | 手动回滚 CRD，`helm rollback` 恢复 |\n| 镜像 tag 不存在 | Pod 进入 `ImagePullBackOff` | `helm rollback` 或修正 image tag 后 `helm upgrade` |\n\n### 4.5 默认值与空值处理\n\n| 字段 | 默认值 | 空值行为 |\n|------|--------|----------|\n| `redis.addr` | `\"\"` | 渲染为空字符串；容器启动失败 |\n| `redis.password` | `\"\"` | 渲染为空字符串；部分 Redis 实例允许无密码 |\n| `router.serviceAccountName` | `\"\"` | 不设置 `serviceAccountName` 字段 (使用 default SA) |\n| `router.rbac.create` | `false` | 不渲染 Router RBAC 资源 |\n| `volcano.scheduler.enabled` | `false` | 不渲染 Volcano 相关资源 |\n| `workloadmanager.extraEnv` | `[]` | 不注入额外环境变量 |\n| `router.extraEnv` | `[]` | 不注入额外环境变量 |\n| `imagePullSecrets` | `[]` | 不设置 `imagePullSecrets` 字段 |\n\n---\n\n## 5. 测试策略 (Testing Strategy)\n\n### 5.1 静态验证 (Static Validation)\n\n#### 5.1.1 Helm Lint\n\n```bash\n# 验证 chart 结构、values 类型、模板语法\nhelm lint manifests/charts/base\n```\n\n预期输出：无 errors，允许 warnings（如 `icon` 字段缺失）。\n\n#### 5.1.2 YAML 语法验证\n\n```bash\n# 验证 values.yaml 为合法 YAML\npython3 -c \"import yaml; yaml.safe_load(open('manifests/charts/base/values.yaml'))\"\n\n# 验证 Chart.yaml 为合法 YAML\npython3 -c \"import yaml; yaml.safe_load(open('manifests/charts/base/Chart.yaml'))\"\n```\n\n### 5.2 模板渲染测试 (Template Rendering Tests)\n\n#### 5.2.1 默认值渲染\n\n```bash\n# 验证默认模板输出包含预期资源\nhelm template test manifests/charts/base | grep -c \"kind: Deployment\"   # 期望: 2\nhelm template test manifests/charts/base | grep -c \"kind: Service\"      # 期望: 2\nhelm template test manifests/charts/base | grep -c \"kind: ClusterRole\"  # 期望: 1\nhelm template test manifests/charts/base | grep -c \"kind: ServiceAccount\" # 期望: 1\n```\n\n#### 5.2.2 关键场景渲染验证\n\n| 场景 | 命令 | 断言 |\n|------|------|------|\n| 默认 WM Deployment | `helm template test manifests/charts/base -s templates/workloadmanager.yaml` | `replicas: 1`, `image: ghcr.io/volcano-sh/workloadmanager:latest` |\n| Redis env 注入 | `helm template test manifests/charts/base --set redis.addr=redis.ns:6379 --set redis.password=secret` | 输出含 `REDIS_ADDR: redis.ns:6379` 和 `REDIS_PASSWORD: secret` |\n| WM 健康探针 | `helm template test manifests/charts/base -s templates/workloadmanager.yaml` | liveness `/health` initialDelay 10s, readiness `/health` initialDelay 5s |\n| Router WORKLOAD_MANAGER_URL | `helm template test manifests/charts/base --namespace agentcube` | `WORKLOAD_MANAGER_URL=http://workloadmanager.agentcube.svc.cluster.local:8080` |\n| Router 健康探针 | `helm template test manifests/charts/base -s templates/agentcube-router.yaml` | liveness `/health/live` initialDelay 1s, readiness `/health/ready` initialDelay 1s |\n| 自定义副本数 | `helm template test manifests/charts/base --set workloadmanager.replicas=3` | `replicas: 3` |\n| 自定义镜像 | `helm template test manifests/charts/base --set workloadmanager.image.repository=myregistry/wm --set workloadmanager.image.tag=v1.2.3` | `image: myregistry/wm:v1.2.3` |\n| extraEnv 注入 | `helm template test manifests/charts/base --set-json 'workloadmanager.extraEnv=[{\"name\":\"CUSTOM\",\"value\":\"val\"}]'` | 输出含 `CUSTOM: val` |\n| Router RBAC 关闭 | `helm template test manifests/charts/base` | 无 Router SA/Role/RoleBinding |\n| Router RBAC 开启 | `helm template test manifests/charts/base --set router.rbac.create=true` | 输出含 Router SA + Role + RoleBinding |\n| Volcano 关闭 | `helm template test manifests/charts/base` | 无 Volcano 资源 |\n| Volcano 开启 | `helm template test manifests/charts/base --set volcano.scheduler.enabled=true` | 输出含 Volcano SA + ConfigMap + ClusterRole + CRB + Service + Deployment |\n| imagePullSecrets | `helm template test manifests/charts/base --set-json 'imagePullSecrets=[{\"name\":\"my-secret\"}]'` | `imagePullSecrets: [{name: my-secret}]` |\n| 命名空间作用域 | `helm template test manifests/charts/base --namespace production` | 所有命名空间资源 `namespace: production` |\n\n#### 5.2.3 CRD 渲染验证\n\n```bash\n# 验证 CRD 包含在模板输出中\nhelm template test manifests/charts/base --include-crds | grep \"kind: CustomResourceDefinition\"\n\n# 验证 AgentRuntime CRD\nhelm template test manifests/charts/base --include-crds | grep \"agentruntimes.runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh\"\n\n# 验证 CodeInterpreter CRD\nhelm template test manifests/charts/base --include-crds | grep \"codeinterpreters.runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh\"\n```\n\n### 5.3 Kubernetes 验证 (Dry-Run)\n\n```bash\n# 默认值 dry-run 验证\nhelm template test manifests/charts/base | kubectl apply --dry-run=client -f -\n\n# 全量 overrides dry-run 验证\nhelm template test manifests/charts/base \\\n  --set redis.addr=redis.ns.svc:6379 \\\n  --set redis.password=secret \\\n  --set volcano.scheduler.enabled=true \\\n  --set router.rbac.create=true \\\n  | kubectl apply --dry-run=client -f -\n```\n\n### 5.4 测试文件布局\n\n```\nmanifests/charts/base/\n├── Chart.yaml\n├── values.yaml\n├── crds/\n│   ├── runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh_agentruntimes.yaml\n│   └── runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh_codeinterpreters.yaml\n└── templates/\n    ├── workloadmanager.yaml\n    ├── agentcube-router.yaml\n    ├── rbac/\n    │   └── workloadmanager.yaml\n    ├── rbac-router.yaml\n    └── volcano-agent-scheduler-development.yaml\n\ntest/chart/                          # Chart 测试脚本 (可选)\n├── test_values.sh                   # values.yaml 结构验证\n├── test_render.sh                   # 模板渲染场景测试\n└── test_crd.sh                      # CRD 验证\n```\n\n### 5.5 测试运行命令\n\n```bash\n# 1. Lint\nhelm lint manifests/charts/base\n\n# 2. 模板渲染验证\nhelm template test manifests/charts/base > /tmp/agentcube-rendered.yaml\n\n# 3. 客户端 dry-run (需要 kubectl 和集群连接)\nkubectl apply --dry-run=client -f /tmp/agentcube-rendered.yaml\n\n# 4. E2E 集成测试 (需要 Kind 集群)\nmake e2e   # 内部调用 test/e2e/run_e2e.sh，包含 helm install 验证\n```\n\n### 5.6 Delta Spec 场景覆盖矩阵\n\n| Delta Spec 场景 | 测试方法 | 验证点 |\n|-----------------|----------|--------|\n| Chart metadata fields | `helm lint` + YAML parse | apiVersion=v1, name=agentcube, version=0.1.0, appVersion=1.0.0 |\n| Default values valid YAML | YAML parse | 所有顶层键存在 |\n| Redis defaults empty strings | values.yaml 读取 | addr=\"\", password=\"\", 含注释 |\n| Router defaults match design | values.yaml 读取 | replicas=1, repo/pullPolicy/tag/service/resources/rbac 全部匹配 |\n| WM defaults match design | values.yaml 读取 | replicas=1, repo/pullPolicy/tag/service/resources 全部匹配 |\n| Volcano disabled by default | values.yaml 读取 | enabled=false |\n| Default WM deployment renders | `helm template` | Deployment name, replicas, image, pullPolicy |\n| WM health probes | `helm template` | liveness/readiness paths and timings |\n| Redis env vars injected | `helm template --set` | REDIS_ADDR, REDIS_PASSWORD in env |\n| AGENTCUBE_NAMESPACE fieldRef | `helm template` | valueFrom.fieldRef.fieldPath: metadata.namespace |\n| extraEnv appended | `helm template --set-json` | custom env vars present |\n| Container args port+runtime | `helm template` | --port=8080, --runtime-class-name= |\n| Resource requests/limits | `helm template` | requests/limits match values |\n| Custom replica count | `helm template --set` | replicas updated |\n| Custom image override | `helm template --set` | image updated |\n| imagePullSecrets applied | `helm template --set-json` | imagePullSecrets in pod spec |\n| Default WM service renders | `helm template` | type/port/targetPort/selector |\n| Custom service type | `helm template --set` | service type updated |\n| Default router deployment | `helm template` | Deployment name, replicas, image |\n| WORKLOAD_MANAGER_URL DNS | `helm template --namespace` | URL with correct namespace and port |\n| Router health probes | `helm template` | /health/live, /health/ready timings |\n| Router args port+debug | `helm template` | --port=8080, --debug |\n| Conditional serviceAccountName | `helm template --set` | SA name set when non-empty |\n| Empty serviceAccountName omitted | `helm template` | no serviceAccountName field |\n| Router extraEnv | `helm template --set-json` | custom env vars present |\n| Default router service | `helm template` | type/port/targetPort/selector |\n| WM RBAC ServiceAccount | `helm template` | SA in release namespace |\n| WM ClusterRole sandbox CRDs | `helm template` | agents.x-k8s.io rules |\n| WM ClusterRole AgentCube CRDs | `helm template` | runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh rules |\n| WM ClusterRole status/finalizers | `helm template` | status/finalizer verbs |\n| WM ClusterRole secrets+tokenreview | `helm template` | secrets full verbs, tokenreviews create |\n| ClusterRoleBinding ties SA | `helm template` | subject and roleRef correct |\n| Router RBAC off by default | `helm template` | no Router RBAC resources |\n| Router RBAC enabled | `helm template --set` | SA+Role+RoleBinding present |\n| Router RBAC custom SA name | `helm template --set` | resources named with custom SA |\n| Router Role secret management | `helm template --set` | secrets full verbs |\n| Volcano disabled by default | `helm template` | no Volcano resources |\n| Volcano enabled | `helm template --set` | SA+ConfigMap+CR+CRB+Service+Deployment |\n| Volcano ConfigMap config | `helm template --set` | agent-scheduler.conf with allocate/predicates/nodeorder |\n| Volcano Deployment replicas+image | `helm template --set` | replicas and image match values |\n| Volcano Deployment args | `helm template --set` | --scheduler-name=agent-scheduler |\n| Volcano Service metrics | `helm template --set` | port 8080, prometheus annotations |\n| AgentRuntime CRD present | `helm template --include-crds` | CRD name, group, version, scope |\n| CodeInterpreter CRD present | `helm template --include-crds` | CRD name, group, version, scope |\n| AgentRuntime required fields | CRD YAML parse | spec.required includes maxSessionDuration, podTemplate, sessionTimeout, targetPort |\n| CodeInterpreter required fields | CRD YAML parse | spec.required includes template, authMode default picod |\n| Namespace scoping | `helm template --namespace` | all namespaced resources use correct namespace |\n| Default naming convention | `helm template` | resource names follow chart defaults |\n| fullnameOverride | `helm template --set` | resource names use override value |\n\n---\n\n## 6. 实现步骤 (Implementation Steps)\n\n### 6.1 文件创建顺序\n\n1. `manifests/charts/base/Chart.yaml` — Chart 元数据 (无依赖)\n2. `manifests/charts/base/values.yaml` — 默认值树 (无依赖)\n3. `manifests/charts/base/crds/runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh_agentruntimes.yaml` — AgentRuntime CRD (依赖 `make gen-crd` 或手工编写)\n4. `manifests/charts/base/crds/runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh_codeinterpreters.yaml` — CodeInterpreter CRD (依赖 `make gen-crd` 或手工编写)\n5. `manifests/charts/base/templates/workloadmanager.yaml` — WM Deployment + Service (依赖 values.yaml)\n6. `manifests/charts/base/templates/agentcube-router.yaml` — Router Deployment + Service (依赖 values.yaml)\n7. `manifests/charts/base/templates/rbac/workloadmanager.yaml` — WM RBAC (无依赖)\n8. `manifests/charts/base/templates/rbac-router.yaml` — 可选 Router RBAC (依赖 values.yaml)\n9. `manifests/charts/base/templates/volcano-agent-scheduler-development.yaml` — 可选 Volcano (依赖 values.yaml)\n\n### 6.2 并行化分组\n\n| 组 | 任务 | 前置条件 |\n|----|------|----------|\n| G1 | Chart.yaml, values.yaml | 无 |\n| G2 | CRD 文件 (2 个) | G1 完成 (目录存在)；或 `make gen-crd` |\n| G3 | workloadmanager.yaml, agentcube-router.yaml | G1 完成 (values.yaml 结构确定) |\n| G4 | rbac/workloadmanager.yaml, rbac-router.yaml, volcano-agent-scheduler-development.yaml | G1 完成 |\n\n### 6.3 验证检查清单\n\n- [ ] `helm lint manifests/charts/base` 无 errors\n- [ ] `helm template test manifests/charts/base` 输出合法 YAML\n- [ ] `helm template test manifests/charts/base | kubectl apply --dry-run=client -f -` 无验证错误\n- [ ] Chart.yaml: apiVersion=v1, name=agentcube, version=0.1.0, appVersion=1.0.0\n- [ ] values.yaml: 所有顶层键存在 (imagePullSecrets, nameOverride, fullnameOverride, redis, router, workloadmanager, volcano)\n- [ ] values.yaml: redis.addr 和 redis.password 默认为 `\"\"`，含安装时必填注释\n- [ ] WM Deployment: replicas, image, pullPolicy, port, env (AGENTCUBE_NAMESPACE fieldRef, REDIS_ADDR, REDIS_PASSWORD, extraEnv), args (--port, --runtime-class-name=), resources, probes, serviceAccountName\n- [ ] WM Service: type, port, targetPort, selector app:workloadmanager\n- [ ] Router Deployment: replicas, conditional serviceAccountName, image, port, env (含 WORKLOAD_MANAGER_URL), args (--port, --debug), resources, probes\n- [ ] Router Service: type, port, targetPort, selector app:agentcube-router\n- [ ] WM RBAC: SA + ClusterRole (完整规则集) + ClusterRoleBinding\n- [ ] Router RBAC: 条件渲染，SA + Role (secrets 全权限) + RoleBinding\n- [ ] Volcano: 条件渲染，SA + ConfigMap + ClusterRole + ClusterRoleBinding + Service + Deployment\n- [ ] CRDs: AgentRuntime + CodeInterpreter 在 crds/ 目录下，group/version/scope 正确\n- [ ] 命名空间: 所有命名空间资源使用 `{{ .Release.Namespace }}`\n- [ ] `--set workloadmanager.replicas=3` 渲染出 replicas: 3\n- [ ] `--set router.rbac.create=true` 渲染出 Router RBAC 资源\n- [ ] `--set volcano.scheduler.enabled=true` 渲染出 Volcano 全套资源\n- [ ] `--set-json 'imagePullSecrets=[{\"name\":\"my-secret\"}]'` 渲染出 imagePullSecrets\n\n---\n\n## 7. 后续变更 (Follow-up Changes)\n\n| 变更 | 依赖关系 | 说明 |\n|------|----------|------|\n| CRD YAML 自动生成 | 依赖 `make gen-crd` | 从 Go 类型 kubebuilder 标记自动生成 CRD，替代手工维护 |\n| Helm 单元测试 (helm-unittest) | 依赖本 AR 完成 | 引入 helm-unittest 插件，将 delta-spec 场景转为自动化测试用例 |\n| Helm 3 apiVersion v2 升级 | 依赖本 AR 完成 | 如需 subchart/library chart 支持，升级 apiVersion 至 v2 |\n| 生产级 values 覆盖文件 | 依赖本 AR 完成 | 为 staging/production 环境创建独立的 values-override.yaml |\n| Helm 仓库发布 | 依赖本 AR 完成 | `helm package` + `helm push` 到 OCI registry 或 ChartMuseum |\n| GitOps 集成 (ArgoCD/Flux) | 依赖本 AR 完成 | 将 chart 作为 HelmRepository + HelmRelease 纳入 GitOps 管理 |\n","filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-